---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';

const title = 'AI 生產力工作坊：目標 × 知識 × 自動化';
const description = '6 小時一日工作坊 — 用 Claude Code + Obsidian 打造目標管理、知識管理、AI 自動化工作流。5 人小班，帶著能跑的系統回家。';

// API base: localhost in dev, production in prod
const API_BASE = import.meta.env.DEV
  ? 'http://localhost:8000'
  : 'https://yu-wenhao-api.calmisland-ea7fe91e.japaneast.azurecontainerapps.io';

const SURVEY_ID = 'workshop-signup-2026-q2';
---

<BaseLayout title={title} description={description} hideLanguageSwitcher={true} noindex={true}>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 lg:py-32 bg-[#F5F1EB]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <p class="text-sm md:text-base font-medium text-[#B8926A] mb-4 tracking-wide uppercase">Workshop</p>
        <h1 class="text-[2rem] md:text-[2.75rem] lg:text-[3.5rem] font-bold text-[#2C2416] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] mb-6">
          AI 生產力工作坊<br /><span class="text-[#5C5144] text-[1.5rem] md:text-[2rem] lg:text-[2.5rem]">目標 × 知識 × 自動化</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl leading-relaxed text-[#5C5144] mb-4">
          一套系統，管時間、管知識、管客戶、管產出。
        </p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#5C5144] mb-4">
          7 小時實作，帶走一套<strong class="text-[#2C2416]">能跑</strong>的 AI 工作系統 — 每天打「開工」3 分鐘就知道今天要做什麼。
        </p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#5C5144] mb-3">
          <strong class="text-[#2C2416]">這套節奏是這堂課的成果，不是賣點。</strong>
        </p>
        <p class="text-base md:text-lg leading-relaxed text-[#8B7355] mb-10">
          不用會寫程式，用說的就好。
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 mb-8">
          <a href="#signup" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 bg-[#B8926A] text-white text-base md:text-lg font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-[#A67D55] hover:shadow-lg hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200">
            填寫報名表
          </a>
          <a href="#outline" class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 border-2 border-[#B8926A] text-[#B8926A] text-base md:text-lg font-medium rounded-full hover:bg-[#B8926A] hover:text-white hover:shadow-md hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200">
            看課程大綱
          </a>
        </div>
        <!-- Quick info badges -->
        <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm text-[#5C5144]">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8926A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
            招募中
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8926A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z"></path></svg>
            7 小時實作 + Office Hour
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8926A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
            限 5 人成班
          </span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 bg-white/60 backdrop-blur px-4 py-2 rounded-full">
            <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8926A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17.657 16.657L13.414 20.9a1.998 1.998 0 01-2.827 0l-4.244-4.243a8 8 0 1111.314 0z"></path><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 11a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0z"></path></svg>
            實體授課
          </span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Solution — 上完課你的早上長這樣 -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-[#2C2416]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-12">
        <h2 class="text-[1.75rem] md:text-[2.25rem] font-bold text-white leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] mb-4">
          上完這堂課，你的工作長這樣
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#C4B9A8] mb-4">
          <strong class="text-white">會議前</strong>：你打「準備明天和客戶 A 的會議」。AI 從你的資料庫拉出過往互動、本週議題、應該帶的資料 — 你拿到一份會議手冊。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#C4B9A8] mb-4">
          <strong class="text-white">會議中</strong>：照會議手冊跑，重點記下來。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-[#C4B9A8] mb-6">
          <strong class="text-white">會議後</strong>：AI 把筆記轉成會議紀錄、抓出 follow-up 待辦、放進你的本週計畫。
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed text-white font-medium">
          你是導演，全部都在掌握中。
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 md:gap-8">
        <div class="bg-[#3D3426] border border-[#5C5144] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#B8926A]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#B8926A]">1</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">目標管理</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#C4B9A8]">把大目標拆成每週行動。不用靠意志力記得追蹤 — AI 每天提醒你進度，每週幫你校正方向。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#3D3426] border border-[#5C5144] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#B8926A]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#B8926A]">2</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">知識 × 客戶管理</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#C4B9A8]">用 Obsidian 建一個找得到東西的資料庫。讀過的文章、開會筆記、客戶資料、靈感想法 — AI 在你需要的時候幫你挖出來。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#3D3426] border border-[#5C5144] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#B8926A]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#B8926A]">3</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">AI 工作流</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#C4B9A8]">Claude Code 不是聊天機器人，是住在你電腦裡的 AI 助理 — 能讀你的檔案、幫你整理資料、自動執行重複工作。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-[#3D3426] border border-[#5C5144] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8">
          <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-xl bg-[#B8926A]/20 flex items-center justify-center mb-5">
            <span class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#B8926A]">4</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-2">會議全流程 × 自動化</p>
          <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#C4B9A8]">會議前 AI 幫你產會議手冊、會議中照本走、會議後自動轉紀錄 + 抓 follow-up 進本週計畫。做一次的事手動做，做三次以上就教 AI 自動跑。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What you'll take home -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-[#FFFDF9]">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-[1.75rem] md:text-[2.25rem] font-bold text-[#2C2416] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] mb-4">
        上完課你帶走什麼
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#5C5144] mb-12">不是投影片，不是筆記。是你電腦裡真的在跑的東西。</p>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#FEF3C7] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#D97706]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 5H7a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2h10a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2h-2M9 5a2 2 0 002 2h2a2 2 0 002-2M9 5a2 2 0 012-2h2a2 2 0 012 2m-6 9l2 2 4-4"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2C2416] mb-2">12 週目標追蹤表</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#5C5144]">3 個目標 + 每週行動清單，AI 每天幫你追蹤進度</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#DBEAFE] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#2563EB]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M19 11H5m14 0a2 2 0 012 2v6a2 2 0 01-2 2H5a2 2 0 01-2-2v-6a2 2 0 012-2m14 0V9a2 2 0 00-2-2M5 11V9a2 2 0 012-2m0 0V5a2 2 0 012-2h6a2 2 0 012 2v2M7 7h10"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2C2416] mb-2">個人資料庫</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#5C5144]">筆記、客戶資料、會議紀錄互相連結，找東西只要兩秒</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#E0E7FF] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#4F46E5]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9.75 17L9 20l-1 1h8l-1-1-.75-3M3 13h18M5 17h14a2 2 0 002-2V5a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2C2416] mb-2">Claude Code AI 助理</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#5C5144]">裝好 + 個人化設定，認識你的工作習慣</p>
        </div>
        <div class="text-center p-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#D1FAE5] flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-[#059669]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path></svg>
          </div>
          <p class="text-lg font-semibold text-[#2C2416] mb-2">2 個自動化指令</p>
          <p class="text-sm text-[#5C5144]">你親手做的，回家打「開工」就能跑</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="mt-12 bg-[#F5F1EB] border border-[#E8E4DD] rounded-2xl p-6 md:p-8 text-center">
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl font-semibold text-[#2C2416]">
          全部串在一起 = 一套隔天就能用的個人工作系統
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Course Outline -->
  <section id="outline" class="py-20 md:py-28 bg-[#F5F1EB]">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
      <h2 class="text-[1.75rem] md:text-[2.25rem] font-bold text-[#2C2416] leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] mb-4">
        課程大綱
      </h2>
      <p class="text-lg text-[#5C5144] mb-12">7 小時實作，從個人工作系統到會議全流程，每個主題都有你親手做的成果帶回家。課後另有 1 小時 Office Hour 開放諮詢。</p>

      <!-- Timeline -->
      <div class="relative">
        <!-- Vertical line -->
        <div class="absolute left-6 md:left-8 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-[#E8E4DD]"></div>

        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Module 1: AI 助理 -->
          <div class="relative flex gap-6 md:gap-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#E0E7FF] flex flex-col items-center justify-center z-10 border-2 border-white shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#4F46E5] leading-none">09:00</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-[#E8E4DD] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 flex-1 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2C2416] mb-2">AI 助理 — 先裝好你的新夥伴</h3>
              <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#5C5144] mb-4">第一件事：在你的電腦裝好 Claude Code — 一個能讀寫你電腦檔案的 AI 助理。教它認識你的工作習慣，寫好個人化設定檔。裝好之後，後面每個模組你都能直接用 AI 來做。</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8926A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-[#B8926A] font-medium">產出：裝好 Claude Code + 個人化設定檔</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Module 2: 目標管理 -->
          <div class="relative flex gap-6 md:gap-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#FEF3C7] flex flex-col items-center justify-center z-10 border-2 border-white shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#D97706] leading-none">10:30</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-[#E8E4DD] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 flex-1 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2C2416] mb-2">找到方向 + 目標管理</h3>
              <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#5C5144] mb-4">釐清你最重要的 3 件事，用 AI 幫你拆成每週具體行動。不是年度計畫那種寫完就忘的東西 — 是每天打開就知道「今天該推哪一步」的追蹤表。</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8926A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-[#B8926A] font-medium">產出：你的 12 週目標追蹤表（3 個目標 + 每週行動清單）</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Lunch -->
          <div class="relative flex gap-6 md:gap-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#F5F1EB] flex items-center justify-center z-10 border-2 border-white shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-xs font-medium text-[#8B7355] leading-none">12:30</span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-center">
              <p class="text-sm text-[#8B7355] italic">午餐 1 小時</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Module 3: 知識管理 -->
          <div class="relative flex gap-6 md:gap-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#DBEAFE] flex flex-col items-center justify-center z-10 border-2 border-white shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#2563EB] leading-none">13:30</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-[#E8E4DD] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 flex-1 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2C2416] mb-2">知識管理 — 找得到東西的資料庫</h3>
              <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#5C5144] mb-4">用 AI 幫你建一個「找得到東西」的個人資料庫。不靠資料夾分類，用連結把筆記、客戶資料、會議紀錄串成網 — 三個月前讀的文章、上次和某客戶聊的內容，需要的時候兩秒就能找到。</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8926A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-[#B8926A] font-medium">產出：你的個人知識庫（完整架構 + 3 篇筆記，互相連結）</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Module 4: 自動化實戰 -->
          <div class="relative flex gap-6 md:gap-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#D1FAE5] flex flex-col items-center justify-center z-10 border-2 border-white shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#059669] leading-none">15:00</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border border-[#E8E4DD] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 flex-1 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2C2416] mb-2">自動化實戰 — 解決你最痛的問題</h3>
              <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#5C5144] mb-4">這個段落會用<strong>你報名時填的工作情境</strong>當案例。我們會挑一個你最痛的工作流（會議前後處理 / 客戶資料整理 / 每日任務管理 / 你自己的場景），現場用 AI 跟著做。</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8926A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-[#B8926A] font-medium">產出：1 個量身打造的自動化指令，回家直接用</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Wrap-up -->
          <div class="relative flex gap-6 md:gap-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#2C2416] flex flex-col items-center justify-center z-10 border-2 border-white shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-white leading-none">16:30</span>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white border-2 border-[#2C2416] rounded-xl p-6 md:p-8 flex-1 shadow-sm">
              <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-[#2C2416] mb-2">收尾：串起來 + 明天就能用</h3>
              <p class="text-base leading-relaxed text-[#5C5144] mb-4">把今天建的四個主題串在一起，現場跑一次完整流程，確認每個人的系統都能動。回家打開電腦就能直接用。</p>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm">
                <svg class="w-4 h-4 text-[#B8926A]" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>
                <span class="text-[#B8926A] font-medium">產出：目標追蹤表 + 個人知識庫 + AI 助理 + 2 個自動化指令 — 全部串在一起，隔天就能用</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Office Hour (Bonus, 不算正式課程) -->
          <div class="relative flex gap-6 md:gap-8">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-12 md:w-16 h-12 md:h-16 rounded-2xl bg-[#FEF3C7] border-2 border-[#D97706] flex flex-col items-center justify-center z-10 shadow-sm">
              <span class="text-xs font-bold text-[#D97706] leading-none">17:00</span>
